chapters.title: SLICE TWO YELLOW MANILA MANGOES (OR USE FROZEN ONES)
CUT ONE SIDE INTO PERPENDICULAR SLICES TO MAKE MINI DICES
PEEL THE REST USING A GLASS CUP
PUT PEELED MANGOES IN A BLENDER
PUT 2 TBSP. MAPLE SYRUP (OR SWEETENER OF CHOICE)
ADD MANGO DICES IN POPSICLE MOLD
